Qingling!

598
00:30:57,830 --> 00:30:58,920
What are you doing?

599
00:30:59,400 --> 00:31:00,110
Let him go.

600
00:31:00,110 --> 00:31:01,520
Sun’er. Help me.

601
00:31:01,830 --> 00:31:02,590
Qingling.

602
00:31:03,160 --> 00:31:04,590
Treating Qingshan like this.

603
00:31:04,710 --> 00:31:06,160
