653
00:33:23,880 --> 00:33:24,760
Mr. Mu.

654
00:33:25,040 --> 00:33:26,640
Can you show me?

655
00:33:30,830 --> 00:33:32,470
If you’re interested,

656
00:33:33,710 --> 00:33:35,000
