796
00:40:04,560 --> 00:40:06,670
You may come here if you need me.

797
00:40:12,910 --> 00:40:13,560
OK.

798
00:40:14,520 --> 00:40:15,390
It’s late.

799
00:40:15,430 --> 00:40:16,360
Let’s go back.

